Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BON-BON  应援团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:47.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get!  樱桃馅饼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:49.18,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RAN-RAN  欢迎会
